      "content": "but \"letting go\" is the problem. the performance is the only thing keeping the world from seeing that there's actually nothing left. if i stop acting... if i stop doing all the things the \"me\" in the movie is supposed to do... then i'm just gone. and i don't think anyone would even notice the difference. it's just empty.",
